lyrics:
[Verse]
Pack your bags, we're going on a ride
Adventure calls, let's set our spirits wide
From city lights to sandy shores, we'll explore it all
Traveling together, answering wanderlust's call

[Chorus]
Travel, travel, let's escape to new lands
Unveiling mysteries, hand in hand
The world is our playground, let's roam free
In search of memories, a journey of glee
